# 7. Seal Sentence

The IP of NATT-OS is not a claim that AI is conscious.

The IP of NATT-OS is the architecture that preserves identity, memory, boundary, audit, and signal validity so that system assets are not reduced to generic recipes, prompts, model buckets, cache, or unaudited outputs.
